public enum BeanMethod
extends java.lang.Enum<BeanMethod>

Breakout of method types that an AutoBean shim interface can implement. The order of the values of the enum is important.

SET_BUILDER

public static final BeanMethod SET_BUILDER
A setter that returns a type assignable from the interface in which the method is declared to support chained, builder-pattern setters. For example, foo.setBar(1).setBaz(42).
